00:02:25.600 --> 00:02:28.120
Isn't it laughable you ask this now?

00:02:31.600 --> 00:02:32.400
Shi'an.

00:02:35.960 --> 00:02:37.520
Please listen to me, Shi'an.

00:02:39.080 --> 00:02:39.880
I admit

00:02:40.440 --> 00:02:42.640
that when my father forced this marriage

00:02:43.480 --> 00:02:44.960
and you favored Concubine Ye,

00:02:45.120 --> 00:02:46.880
I felt wronged.

00:02:47.120 --> 00:02:48.400
That's why I treated you coldly.

00:02:50.200 --> 00:02:51.280
But I'll change.

00:02:52.520 --> 00:02:54.160
I won't treat you as I did before.

00:02:55.400 --> 00:02:57.400
Don't you prefer Ye Qinglan's demeanor?

00:02:57.800 --> 00:02:59.440
I can do as she did.

00:03:00.560 --> 00:03:02.160
Give me one more chance, please?

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:08.520
After all the harm you caused A'man,

00:03:12.440 --> 00:03:14.320
