00:03:16.200 --> 00:03:16.680
Step aside.

00:03:17.440 --> 00:03:18.240
Lu Shi'an!

00:03:22.600 --> 00:03:26.120
Is there not a shred of love for me
in your heart?

00:03:27.520 --> 00:03:28.160
